import PyPDF2

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/20-CAD/context-aware-decoding-main/paper.pdf'
with open(pdf_path, 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    num_pages = len(reader.pages)
    text = ''
    for i in range(min(num_pages, 10)):
        text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n\n'
print(text[:3000])
